                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9005" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0221</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1103 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">平台赋能，数据助力：“檬豆科技”推动中小企业转型升级</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Platform empowerment and data assistance: Mengdou Technology promotes the transformation and upgrading of small and medium-sized enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">韩民，刘玮，高欣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（华东）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛檬豆网络科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链数字化；平台采购；供应链金融；转型升级</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">supply chain digitalization; platform procurement; supply chain finance; transformation and upgrading</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小企业高质量发展是国民经济快速、持续、稳定增长的坚实基础和重要力量。目前我国中小型制造企业普遍存在着采购成本高、技术创新慢、智能制造量级重、融资难度高的四大难题。青岛檬豆网络科技有限公司将中小企业作为服务对象，利用柠檬豆工业互联网平台构建了“四朵云”，从集中采购帮助企业降低成本出发，到助力企业科技创新和数智化转型，再到创新供应链金融模式帮助企业融资，解决了长期困扰中小企业的四大供应链难题。檬豆科技搭建的数字化生态服务体系全面促进了中小企业转型升级，实现高质量发展。本案例旨在探究数字平台企业如何通过推动供应链数字化创新产品及服务模式，如何利用数字技术及数据要素创新供应链金融业务模式及风险管理方式。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The high-quality development of small and medium-sized enterprises is a solid foundation and an important force for the rapid, sustained and stable growth of the national economy. At present, SMEs in China generally have four major problems: high procurement costs, slow technological innovation, heavy intelligent manufacturing, and difficult financing. Qingdao Mengdou Network Technology Co., Ltd. takes SMEs as the service object, and uses the lemon bean industrial Internet platform to build &quot;four clouds&quot;, starting from centralized procurement to help enterprises reduce costs, to help enterprises in scientific and technological innovation and digital and intelligent transformation, and then to innovate the supply chain financial model to help enterprises finance, solves the four major supply chain problems that have plagued SMEs for a long time. The digital ecological service system built by Mengdou Technology has comprehensively promoted the transformation and upgrading of SMEs and achieved high-quality development. This case study aims to explore how digital platform enterprises can innovate product and service models by promoting supply chain digitalization, and how to use digital technology and data elements to innovate supply chain finance business models and risk management tools.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链数字化；供应链金融与风险管理；数字平台建设</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
